frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature figures in red uniforms surrounding a large lemon tart. The figures appear to be working together to pour lemon juice onto the tart, with some pulling carts filled with lemons and raspberries. The tart is decorated with lemon slices and powdered sugar, creating a playful and imaginative setting.
